<p>i have read some articles about that and read the node_example module.<br />
thank you Mile23 for telling me about entities.</p>
<p>so we should define standard entities to share between our modules.<br />
defining fields to use like :<br />
for users : grid / map / uuid / name...<br />
for grids : name, loginuri...<br />
etc...</p>
<p>maybe there is already an international standard about storing virtual world user informations... i don t know<br />
like a postal address, usually, there are : name , street, street number, town, zip code<br />
but for avatars...</p>
